                    <div class="col-lg-7 col-md-7 col-sm-7  col-xs-7 pr-0 line1">
                        <span> 8 nov </span> - Important Message regarding changes due to
                        Coronavirus.
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-2 col-md-4 col-sm-4">
                        <img src="~/Content/assets/images/main-chevlon.svg" width="20">
